topik tesisku.

235
00:17:54,656 --> 00:17:57,392
Aku tahu dan itu bisa...

236
00:17:59,162 --> 00:18:01,431
Bisa menginspirasi, 'kan ?

237
00:18:03,265 --> 00:18:04,599
Benar ?

238
00:18:08,638 --> 00:18:10,739
Apa ada kelab seks
di Stockholm...

239
00:18:10,873 --> 00:18:13,176
...yang harus kita kunjungi
sebelum ke utara ?

240
00:18:13,308 --> 00:18:14,977
Tidak, kita
langsung ke utara.

241
00:18:16,679 --> 00:18:18,148
Tidak langsung sampai, 'kan ?

242
00:18:18,280 --> 00:18:19,182
Kita harus lewat Stockholm...

243
00:18:19,314 --> 00:18:20,382
...sebelum ke sana.

244
00:18:20,515 --> 00:18:21,484
Tidak, arahnya beda.

245
00:18:21,617 --> 00:18:23,619
Stockholm ada
di selatan Arlanda.

246
00:18:23,753 --> 00:18:25,089
Ada Dani.

247
00:18:25,221 --> 00:18:26,621
Dia mau naik.

248
00:18:28,223 --> 00:18:29,559
Baik.

249
00:18:29,692 --> 00:18:32,562
Ini perlu dibereskan ?
/ Tak usah.

250
00:18:40,636 --> 00:18:43,505
Kuundang Dani ke Swedia.

251
00:18:44,073 --> 00:18:46,042
Sekadar info.

252
00:18:46,175 --> 00:18:47,510
Dia tak ikut...,

253
00:18:47,643 --> 00:18:50,312
...tapi kuundang saja
supaya tak canggung.

254
00:18:51,948 --> 00:18:54,350
Kau mengundangnya...

255
00:18:55,051 --> 00:18:56,686
Tapi dia tak ikut.

256
00:18:58,188 --> 00:18:59,555
Dia tak mau ?

257
00:19:01,491 --> 00:19:04,393
Kuundang dan
dia menerimanya...,

258
00:19:04,527 --> 00:19:07,429
...tapi dia tak ikut
ke Swedia.

259
00:19:08,064 --> 00:19:09,332
Baik.

260
00:19:11,801 --> 00:19:13,871
Kalian tahu apa
yang dia lalui.

261
00:19:15,037 --> 00:19:18,374
Ya, Kawan,
kukira itu...

262
00:19:18,508 --> 00:19:19,910
Tak ada yang keberatan.

263
00:19:20,043 --> 00:19:21,812
Kukira kau mengatakan
hal lain.

264
00:19:21,945 --> 00:19:23,579
Baik, bagus.

265
00:19:24,814 --> 00:19:28,284
Supaya jelas, kalian
menyuruhku mengundangnya...

266
00:19:28,417 --> 00:19:29,586
...dan kalian tahu
dia akan ikut.

267
00:19:29,720 --> 00:19:30,953
Sepakat ?

268
00:19:31,087 --> 00:19:32,256
Ya.

269
00:19:32,388 --> 00:19:33,990
Hei !
/ Hei, Sayang !

270
00:19:35,225 --> 00:19:36,392
Hei, Teman - teman.

271
00:19:36,526 --> 00:19:38,293
Hei.
/ Hei.

272
00:19:38,427 --> 00:19:39,862
Sedang apa ?

273
00:19:41,497 --> 00:19:42,732
Bersantai.

274
00:19:42,866 --> 00:19:44,001
Bagus.

275
00:19:46,469 --> 00:19:48,471
Jadi, Swedia.

276
00:19:48,604 --> 00:19:50,073
Ya.
/ Kau ikut, 'kan ?

277
00:19:50,207 --> 00:19:52,142
Aku...

278
00:19:52,276 --> 00:19:53,544
Kurasa begitu...,

279
00:19:53,677 --> 00:19:55,578
...kalau tak ganggu
rencana kalian.

280
00:19:55,711 --> 00:19:57,847
Tidak.
/ Tidak sama sekali.

281
00:20:02,518 --> 00:20:04,520
Christian, bisa lihat...

282
00:20:04,654 --> 00:20:06,455
...paragraf ini sebentar ?

283
00:20:07,291 --> 00:20:09,760
Tentu.

284
00:20:10,793 --> 00:20:12,628
Sebentar.

285
00:20:17,835 --> 00:20:19,602
Hei, Pelle
/ Hai.

286
00:20:28,178 --> 00:20:29,947
Kau gambar apa ?

287
00:20:30,080 --> 00:20:31,315
Cuma meja.

288
00:20:34,117 --> 00:20:35,085
Bagaimana keadaanmu ?

289
00:20:35,685 --> 00:20:37,020
Lumayan baik.
/ Ya ?

290
00:20:37,154 --> 00:20:40,023
Selesai UAS.

291
00:20:40,157 --> 00:20:42,658
Kau sendiri ?

292
00:20:42,792 --> 00:20:44,094
Aku belum selesai...,

293
00:20:44,228 --> 00:20:47,831
...tapi aku diberi
cuti tahun ini.

294
00:20:47,965 --> 00:20:50,234
Astaga, benar.
Maaf.

295
00:20:50,366 --> 00:20:51,634
Itu...

296
00:20:51,767 --> 00:20:53,670
Kau suka jurusan
Antropologi ?

297
00:20:54,204 --> 00:20:55,505
Aku menyukainya.

298
00:20:55,639 --> 00:20:57,641
Lebih suka daripada dia.

299
00:21:00,310 --> 00:21:02,012
Kau jurusan psikiatri, 'kan ?

300
00:21:02,145 --> 00:21:03,413
Psikologi.

301
00:21:03,547 --> 00:21:05,916
Baik.
/ Makanya aku gila.

302
00:21:06,050 --> 00:21:08,218
Kelihatan dari mata konyolmu.

303
00:21:09,987 --> 00:21:11,955
Jadi ikut ke Halsingland ?

304
00:21:12,089 --> 00:21:13,291
Sepertinya.

305
00:21:13,423 --> 00:21:16,827
Kita akan tiba
di hari ultahku.

306
00:21:16,960 --> 00:21:19,429
Selamat ulang tahun.
/ Terima kasih.

307
00:21:19,563 --> 00:21:24,334
Christian bilang kalian
punya rencana pekan ini.

308
00:21:24,467 --> 00:21:26,003
Ya, semacam...

309
00:21:26,136 --> 00:21:27,871
...festival keluargaku
selama sembilan hari.

310
00:21:28,005 --> 00:21:29,941
Banyak arak - arakan...,

311
00:21:30,074 --> 00:21:31,842
...upacara istimewa,
dan memakai kostum.

312
00:21:31,975 --> 00:21:33,443
Terdengar seru.

313
00:21:33,577 --> 00:21:35,380
Mungkin terlihat konyol.

314
00:21:35,512 --> 00:21:37,748
Seperti teater.

315
00:21:37,882 --> 00:21:39,082
Christian bilang kau...

316
00:21:39,216 --> 00:21:41,952
...dari komune, 'kan ?

317
00:21:42,085 --> 00:21:44,188
Ya, kami komunitas kecil.

318
00:21:45,223 --> 00:21:47,124
Akan kutunjukkan.

319
00:21:54,264 --> 00:21:56,667
Aku bisa melihat
arak - arakannya.

320
00:21:56,800 --> 00:21:58,035
Kami membuat
pakaian istimewa...

321
00:21:58,169 --> 00:22:00,238
...setiap titik balik matahari
musim dingin dan panas.

322
00:22:00,371 --> 00:22:03,340
Semua orang ikut berperan.

323
00:22:03,473 --> 00:22:04,942
Simbol menarik.

324
00:22:05,075 --> 00:22:08,346
Ya, kami diajari
alfabet Rune.

325
00:22:08,478 --> 00:22:10,647
Siapa itu ?

326
00:22:10,781 --> 00:22:13,217
Itu Ratu Mei tahun lalu.

327
00:22:14,118 --> 00:22:15,452
Cantik.

328
00:22:16,653 --> 00:22:19,456
Aku senang kau ikut.

329
00:22:20,991 --> 00:22:23,895
Kurasa baik untukmu.

330
00:22:24,461 --> 00:22:25,997
Terima kasih.

331
00:22:27,097 --> 00:22:28,598
Aku juga...

332
00:22:28,732 --> 00:22:30,368
...tak sempat mengatakannya...,

333
00:22:30,500 --> 00:22:33,037
...tapi aku...

334
00:22:33,171 --> 00:22:36,707
...turut berduka
atas kehilanganmu.

335
00:22:37,507 --> 00:22:40,178
Kejadian itu...,

336
00:22:40,311 --> 00:22:42,012
...tak bisa kubayangkan.

337
00:22:42,512 --> 00:22:43,714
Maksudku...

338
00:22:43,847 --> 00:22:45,482
Ortuku juga sudah tiada.
/ Baik.

339
00:22:45,615 --> 00:22:47,151
Aku sedikit paham perasaanmu.

340
00:22:47,285 --> 00:22:48,753
Maaf.
/ Tidak.

341
00:22:48,886 --> 00:22:50,253
Maafkan aku.
/ Tidak, kau...

342
00:22:50,388 --> 00:22:52,823
Aku mau
ke kamar mandi.

343
00:23:43,141 --> 00:23:44,976
<i>Para penumpang...,</i>

344
00:23:45,109 --> 00:23:48,179
<i>...kita akan mulai turun
ke Stockholm...</i>

345
00:23:56,988 --> 00:24:00,024
Ya ampun,
wanita di sini.

346
00:24:00,158 --> 00:24:02,060
Kenapa mereka
semua seksi ?

347
00:24:02,193 --> 00:24:03,828
Kaum Viking membawa
wanita terbaik...

348
00:24:03,961 --> 00:24:07,231
...dari negara lain ke sini.

349
00:24:07,366 --> 00:24:09,700
Christian, kau bisa
bahas di tesismu.

350
00:24:09,834 --> 00:24:11,302
Berapa lama perjalanannya ?

351
00:24:11,436 --> 00:24:12,470
Sekitar empat jam.

352
00:24:12,603 --> 00:24:14,605
Astaga.

353
00:25:21,373 --> 00:25:23,774
Ini pemberhentian pertama.

354
00:25:23,908 --> 00:25:25,009
Ini tempatnya ?

355
00:25:25,144 --> 00:25:27,112
Bukan, hampir sampai.

356
00:25:32,284 --> 00:25:33,385
Pelle !

357
00:25:34,086 --> 00:25:35,254
Hei !
/ Hei !

358
00:25:35,387 --> 00:25:36,822
Indah sekali.
/ Ya ampun.

359
00:25:36,955 --> 00:25:37,756
Mereka pemuda...

360
00:25:37,889 --> 00:25:39,224
...dari desaku.

361
00:25:39,358 --> 00:25:41,326
Mereka juga baru
kembali dari perjalanan.

362
00:25:41,759 --> 00:25:43,061
Ikutlah.

363
00:25:44,631 --> 00:25:46,030
Hei !

364
00:25:46,164 --> 00:25:48,333
Ini teman - temanku
dari Amerika.

365
00:25:50,668 --> 00:25:52,804
Ya ampun.
/ Hei.

366
00:25:52,938 --> 00:25:54,239
Jalanlah.

367
00:25:54,373 --> 00:25:55,706
Banyak serangga.

368
00:25:55,840 --> 00:25:57,409
Indah, 'kan ?

369
00:26:03,881 --> 00:26:04,917
Jadi ini...

370
00:26:05,050 --> 00:26:06,418
...Mark, Dani...,
/ Hai.

371
00:26:06,552 --> 00:26:09,154
...Christian dan Josh.

372
00:26:09,289 --> 00:26:10,955
Apa ?

373
00:26:11,089 --> 00:26:13,792
Sebentar.

374
00:26:13,926 --> 00:26:15,294
Dia kenal orang itu ?

375
00:26:15,427 --> 00:26:16,362
Dia terdengar marah.

376
00:26:27,272 --> 00:26:28,373
Itu pertanda baik.

377
00:26:34,112 --> 00:26:36,348
Kemarilah.

378
00:26:36,481 --> 00:26:39,284
Ini teman - temanku
dari Amerika.

379
00:26:39,419 --> 00:26:40,386
Christian, Dani...,

380
00:26:40,520 --> 00:26:41,852
...Josh, dan Mark.
/ Hai.

381
00:26:41,987 --> 00:26:43,488
Perkenalkan saudaraku, Ingemar.

382
00:26:43,622 --> 00:26:45,525
Bersahabat sejak bayi.

383
00:26:45,658 --> 00:26:46,825
Ya.

384
00:26:46,959 --> 00:26:50,028
Jadi, Christian,
Josh, Mark...,

385
00:26:50,162 --> 00:26:51,363
...Dani ?
/ Ya.

386
00:26:51,496 --> 00:26:53,465
Bagus.
Perkenalkan teman - temanku.

387
00:26:53,600 --> 00:26:55,000
Ini Simon dan Connie...

388
00:26:55,133 --> 00:26:56,636
...dari London.
/ Apa kabar ?

389
00:26:56,768 --> 00:26:58,769
Hai.
/ Simon, ini Pelle...

390
00:26:58,904 --> 00:27:00,939
...dan teman - temannya...

391
00:27:01,073 --> 00:27:02,475
...yang baru kutemui.

392
00:27:04,677 --> 00:27:05,911
Waktunya pas sekali.

393
00:27:06,044 --> 00:27:08,715
Kami baru mengambilnya.

394
00:27:08,847 --> 00:27:10,882
Belum kami makan.

395
00:27:11,451 --> 00:27:13,152
Astaga.

396
00:27:13,286 --> 00:27:16,088
Mau makan sekarang atau
beres - beres dulu ?

397
00:27:16,221 --> 00:27:17,557
Ayo makan sekarang.

398
00:27:17,690 --> 00:27:19,024
Ya.
/ Bagus.

399
00:27:19,525 --> 00:27:20,927
Kau tahu...,

400
00:27:21,060 --> 00:27:23,895
...aku mau lihat
pemandangan dulu.

401
00:27:24,029 --> 00:27:26,499
Ya, tentu.
/ Baik.

402
00:27:26,633 --> 00:27:28,167
Kalau kau merasa gelisah...,

403
00:27:28,301 --> 00:27:30,002
...jangan dimakan

404
00:27:30,135 --> 00:27:32,572
Tidak.
Aku mau adaptasi dulu.

405
00:27:32,705 --> 00:27:34,139
Baik.
/ Baik.

406
00:27:35,341 --> 00:27:37,110
Akan kutunggu.
/ Tidak, duluan saja.

407
00:27:37,243 --> 00:27:38,543
Tidak, kutunggu.
/ Duluan saja.

408
00:27:38,678 --> 00:27:40,312
Kita makan bersama.

409
00:27:40,446 --> 00:27:42,582
Siap ?
/ Mengerti ?

410
00:27:42,715 --> 00:27:45,451
Aku akan tunggu Dani,
duluan saja.

411
00:27:47,453 --> 00:27:49,622
Tak bisa dimakan
di waktu berbeda...,

412
00:27:49,756 --> 00:27:51,324
...nanti sensasinya terpisah.

413
00:27:52,992 --> 00:27:54,960
Kalian mau tunggu kami ?

414
00:28:01,100 --> 00:28:02,367
Ya sudah.

415
00:28:02,502 --> 00:28:04,069
Sayang, jangan.
/ Aku siap.

416
00:28:04,202 --> 00:28:05,471
Tak apa.
/ Jangan buru - buru.

417
00:28:05,605 --> 00:28:07,440
Tidak.
Aku sudah siap.

418
00:28:08,908 --> 00:28:10,342
Yakin ?

419
00:28:12,077 --> 00:28:14,147
Ya, Mark.
Terima kasih.

420
00:28:14,280 --> 00:28:15,948
Mereka membuat teh jamur.

421
00:28:16,082 --> 00:28:17,483
Kalau tak suka rasanya.

422
00:28:17,618 --> 00:28:19,951
Baik.
Kucoba yang itu.

423
00:28:20,085 --> 00:28:21,421
Ingemar ? Ingemar ?
/ Ingemar.

424
00:28:21,554 --> 00:28:23,456
Ingemar. Terima kasih.
/ Bagus.

425
00:28:25,091 --> 00:28:26,158
Jangan biarkan Mark...

426
00:28:26,291 --> 00:28:27,427
...memaksamu.
/ Tidak.

427
00:28:27,560 --> 00:28:29,362
Dibanding yang lain.
/ Tidak.

428
00:28:29,495 --> 00:28:30,798
Nanti suasana jadi rusak.

429
00:28:30,930 --> 00:28:32,498
Kau siap ?
/ Ya, terima kasih.

430
00:28:32,633 --> 00:28:34,032
Silakan.

431
00:28:34,166 --> 00:28:35,201
Terima kasih.

432
00:28:35,335 --> 00:28:37,003
Kita mulai.

433
00:28:37,136 --> 00:28:38,438
Bayangkan hal menyenangkan.
/ Kau yakin ?

434
00:28:38,571 --> 00:28:40,774
Ya. Aku senang.
/ Makanlah.

435
00:28:42,575 --> 00:28:44,510
Baik.
/ Ya ?

436
00:28:44,644 --> 00:28:45,945
Kau yakin ?

437
00:28:46,079 --> 00:28:48,047
Ini pasti seru.

438
00:28:48,181 --> 00:28:50,216
Siap ?
/ Ya, mulai.

439
00:28:55,254 --> 00:28:56,889
Pukul berapa ini ?

440
00:28:57,023 --> 00:29:00,159
Pukul 21:00.

441
00:29:02,095 --> 00:29:03,497
Apa ?

442
00:29:05,098 --> 00:29:06,532
Apa ?

443
00:29:07,866 --> 00:29:10,036
Mustahil !
Langit masih biru !

444
00:29:11,003 --> 00:29:13,106
Tenang, ini Swedia.

445
00:29:13,240 --> 00:29:16,175
Itu tak normal.
Kenapa begitu ?

446
00:29:16,309 --> 00:29:19,112
Tenang, Mark.
Itu matahari tengah malam.

447
00:29:19,245 --> 00:29:21,448
Rasanya aneh.
Aku tak menyukainya !

448
00:29:21,582 --> 00:29:23,683
Ini normal.

449
00:29:23,817 --> 00:29:25,051
Aku merasa tak baik.

450
00:29:25,184 --> 00:29:26,854
Astaga, orang baru.

451
00:29:26,986 --> 00:29:28,087
Apa ?

452
00:29:28,221 --> 00:29:30,490
Aku tak mau
ada orang baru.

453
00:29:30,623 --> 00:29:33,426
Orang baru itu
bagus, Mark.

454
00:29:34,561 --> 00:29:35,895
Hai !

455
00:29:39,065 --> 00:29:40,199
Aku akan berbaring.

456
00:29:40,333 --> 00:29:41,735
Ya, berbaringlah.

457
00:29:41,869 --> 00:29:43,936
Semuanya berbaring.

458
00:29:47,006 --> 00:29:49,142
Lakukanlah.
Rasanya nyaman.

459
00:29:52,212 --> 00:29:54,213
Josh, bisa berbaring ?

460
00:29:55,948 --> 00:29:57,584
Kau bisa merasakannya ?

461
00:29:58,184 --> 00:29:59,553
Energi.

462
00:29:59,686 --> 00:30:01,121
Dari Bumi.

463
00:30:15,135 --> 00:30:16,905
Lihat !

464
00:30:17,037 --> 00:30:19,439
Pohonnya bernapas.

465
00:30:26,279 --> 00:30:28,715
Alam tahu bagaimana cara...

466
00:30:28,849 --> 00:30:30,684
...agar tetap harmonis.

467
00:30:33,120 --> 00:30:36,390
Semua melakukan perannya.

468
00:30:43,730 --> 00:30:46,166
Kalian seperti keluargaku.

469
00:30:49,036 --> 00:30:51,738
Seperti keluarga kandung.

470
00:30:53,707 --> 00:30:55,175
Dani ?

471
00:30:57,977 --> 00:30:59,212
Maaf.

472
00:30:59,346 --> 00:31:02,416
Aku mau jalan - jalan.

473
00:31:02,549 --> 00:31:04,184
Aku juga.

474
00:31:04,318 --> 00:31:06,954
Aku sendiri saja.

475
00:31:09,456 --> 00:31:11,325
Tidak.

476
00:31:12,159 --> 00:31:13,794
Jangan pikirkan itu.

477
00:31:13,927 --> 00:31:15,329
Sebentar lagi kau ultah.

478
00:31:15,462 --> 00:31:18,967
Kau baik saja.

479
00:31:28,408 --> 00:31:31,043
Hentikan.
Aku baik saja.

480
00:31:31,178 --> 00:31:32,779
Hei, Dani !

481
00:31:35,583 --> 00:31:36,784
Bagaimana keadaanmu ?

482
00:31:38,084 --> 00:31:39,753
Mereka menertawakanku.

483
00:31:39,887 --> 00:31:43,090
Apa ? Tidak.
Pasti tidak.

484
00:31:43,892 --> 00:31:45,426
Mereka hanya tertawa.

485
00:31:46,193 --> 00:31:48,195
Mau ketemu teman - temanku ?

486
00:31:51,098 --> 00:31:54,701
Maaf, terima kasih.

487
00:32:00,307 --> 00:32:04,378
Hentikan ! Astaga !

488
00:32:07,782 --> 00:32:11,251
Kau baik saja.

489
00:32:47,187 --> 00:32:48,590
Hei.

490
00:32:55,930 --> 00:32:57,664
